name: Norwegian Long Haul 787-8 [EI-LNB] Taxi and RTO at Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everybody, here's Norwegian Long Haul's 2nd 787 doing a rejected takeoff at Paine Field. I saw -LNB a lot during my last few days at Paine, so I got lots of footage of her. The tail has since been painted, and she's now flying with Norwegian. Sadly, I only have a few Paine Field videos left :( Hope you guys enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
